{"tid":900952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(美國) 共和黨律師幫CNN打官司, 起訴特朗普政府","createTime":"2018-11-13T15:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T04:00:40.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d72d2ae92007c3049f534b9e9eee2d5aa2891e4","tid":900952,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"CNN宣布聘用共和黨律師Theodore Olson, 入稟控告美國政府, 就白宮撤銷其首席駐白宮記者採訪證一事, 要求法院發出禁制令. <br />\n<br />\nTheodore Olson係共和黨成員, 曾經為共和黨總統 George W. Bush效力, 而家竟然調轉槍頭. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/CNNPR/status/1062356810903027712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCNNPR%2Fstatus%2F1062356810903027712&d=7M2MF2%2FQfIbUl1XzgL2gNjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7e212e9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCNNPR%2Fstatus%2F1062356810903027712&h=ba31eddd\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/CNNPR/status/1062356810903027712</a><br />\n<br />\nStatement from Ted Olson, attorney for CNN and @Acosta:<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/13/233516_39af30ca1cd8df815d99ba39d5e9f34b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F13%2F233516_39af30ca1cd8df815d99ba39d5e9f34b.jpg&h=efc18fe3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8e0f7718c5a561c55367d944b8a000c2ec8b986","tid":900952,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"有關共和黨人Theodore Olson既詳細資歷<br />\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theodore_Olson\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTheodore_Olson&d=7M2MF2%2FQfIbUl1XzgL2gNjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c84d5324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theodore_Olson</a>"},{"pid":"845f489f234c1d41d5f350b6408df18fb5049842","tid":900952,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:39:13.000Z","msg":"毒果報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181113/58909854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181113%2F58909854&d=7M2MF2%2FQfIbUl1XzgL2gNjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=46047b7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181113%2F58909854&h=ed151cb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181113/58909854</a><br />\n<br />\n 【挑戰侵侵】不滿褫奪旗下記者採訪證　CNN向政府提出訴訟<br />\n<br />\n(路透社)<br />\n(路透社)<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1113 22:47<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）周二入稟控告美國政府，就白宮撤銷其首席駐白宮記者阿科斯塔（Jim Acosta）採訪證一事，要求法院發出禁制令。<br />\n<br />\nCNN在聲明中要求「法院立即頒令，歸還採訪證予阿科斯塔」，「行動今次針對CNN和阿科斯塔，亦可能發生在任何人身上，如果不作出挑戰，白宮的行為會對政治記者造成危險的寒蟬效應。」<br />\n<br />\nCNN指白宮的行為違反保障新聞自由、表達自由的《美國憲法》第一及第五修正案，CNN及阿科斯塔為原訴人，特朗普、幕僚長凱利、白宮發言人桑德斯等一眾官員為被告。<br />\n<br />\n阿科斯塔在本月中期選舉結束後的首個記者會上，向特朗普提問有關中美洲難民問題，結果令特朗普大動肝火。一名白宮女實習生試圖從阿科斯塔手上奪去麥克風，他狀似撥開她的手，並繼續追問通俄門，特朗普怒斥他「無禮、惹人討厭」。其後白宮發言人桑德斯指責阿科斯塔粗暴對該名女實習生，故撤銷其白宮通行證。<br />\n<br />\n但有美媒揭發桑德斯指是證據的片段，曾被右翼網站加工，有數格片段重複播放，疑似將阿科斯塔的動作加快和放大，讓他看似大力推開該實習生，而非拿回麥克風。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"cfab6cd2d64b6fc7208dd84d890c3e968d6b7983","tid":900952,"uid":34572,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"又一個將香港嗰套套落美國嘅二元對立傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd088c8ca3437a7a9432ec3b3ada7ec72be69210","tid":900952,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"cfab6cd2d64b6fc7208dd84d890c3e968d6b7983","tid":900952,"uid":34572,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"又一個將香港嗰套套落美國嘅二元對立傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"唔少連登仔將社會問題歸於 <strong>左 VS 右</strong> 二元對立.<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍都俾人話係極左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/215135/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/215135/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5ac2419108c519ab53a8c50598984367ebdde282","tid":900952,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cfab6cd2d64b6fc7208dd84d890c3e968d6b7983","tid":900952,"uid":34572,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:40:55.000Z","msg":"又一個將香港嗰套套落美國嘅二元對立傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T23:16:38.000Z","msg":"學晒教主嗰套<br />\n你唔支持我<br />\n我就要反你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0e6d8d0afe309f0d42aab3eb2db3536b67825f","tid":900952,"uid":28624,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T23:34:58.000Z","msg":"你係度搞事串人屌人先<br />\n搞亂個會場俾人踢走<br />\n然後話人地極權損害自由<br />\nCnn民主黨班友真係滑稽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712a64e760c92c4a2a80f17002f4c2de141d35a6","tid":900952,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf0e6d8d0afe309f0d42aab3eb2db3536b67825f","tid":900952,"uid":28624,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T23:34:58.000Z","msg":"你係度搞事串人屌人先<br />\n搞亂個會場俾人踢走<br />\n然後話人地極權損害自由<br />\nCnn民主黨班友真係滑稽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T23:41:23.000Z","msg":"Theodore Olson係共和黨人, 唔係民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n親侵網站newsmax報導: Donald Trump曾邀請Theodore Olson入政府做野, 但Theodore Olson拒絕<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.newsmax.com/politics/trump-legal-team-theodore-olson/2018/03/20/id/849743/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsmax.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-legal-team-theodore-olson%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2Fid%2F849743%2F&d=7M2MF2%2FQfIbUl1XzgL2gNjQ9OVC7k